text: The State symbols of the Eastern Republic of Uruguay are the symbols that are used to represent the Uruguayan people proper and abroad to represent the country and its people. ==Uruguayan symbols== Symbol Image Coat of arms Coat of arms of Uruguay Flag Flag of Uruguay Flower National flower of Uruguay Erythrina crista-galli Tree National tree of Uruguay Erythrina crista-galli Plant National plant of Uruguay Cortaderia jubata Bird National bird of Uruguay Vanellus chilensis lampronotus Animal National animal of Uruguay Leopardus colocola munoai Fruit National fruit of Uruguay Vaccinium myrtillus ===Related pages=== * National symbols of Paraguay
title: National symbols of Uruguay
